summary: Moves the skyforge chest to an unreachable spot
descriptionHtml:
For people who don't know you can escape whiterun by jumping on a barrel and jumping out the city or whirlwind sprinting off jorrvaskr and can loot everything eorlund greymane is currently selling and his gold

The unofficial skyrim patch did not fix the location of the skyforge chest. They moved the barrel to prevent you from jumping out white run but did not move the chest. There Is still the  way of gettinf to it aswell by whirlwind sprinting off of jorrvaskr. I did not fix the glitch to escape whiterun however I did move down the chest so you cant loot it.
author: BaconBeast69
